msgstr "请参阅以下演示："

#: ../../source/faq.rst:214
msgid ""
"How to understand difference between ``tc.array_to_tensor`` and "
"``tc.backend.convert_to_tensor``?"
msgstr "如何理解 ``tc.array_to_tensor`` 和 ``tc.backend.convert_to_tensor`` 之间的区别？"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:216
msgid ""
"``tc.array_to_tensor`` converts one or multiple arrays to tensors and "
"automatically casts them to the default dtype of TensorCircuit-NG (i.e., "
"``tc.dtypestr``). It also supports specifying a specific dtype and can "
"handle multiple inputs: ``a_tensor, b_tensor = "
"tc.array_to_tensor(a_array, b_array)``."
msgstr "``tc.array_to_tensor`` 将一个或多个数组转换为张量，并自动将其转换为 TensorCircuit-NG 的默认数据类型（即 ``tc.dtypestr``）。它还支持指定特定数据类型，并能处理多个输入：``a_tensor, b_tensor = tc.array_to_tensor(a_array, b_array)``。"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:218
msgid ""
"In contrast, ``tc.backend.convert_to_tensor`` is a lower-level API that "
"converts a single array into a tensor for the active backend. By default,"
" it preserves the input's dtype, but it now also supports an optional "
"``dtype`` argument to specify the desired type during conversion."
msgstr "相比之下，``tc.backend.convert_to_tensor`` 是一个更底层的 API，用于将单个数组转换为当前后端的张量。默认情况下，它保留输入的 dtype，但现在也支持可选的 ``dtype`` 参数以在转换时指定目标类型。"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:222
msgid ""
"How to arrange the circuit gate placement in the visualization from "
"``c.tex()``?"
msgstr "如何在 ``c.tex()`` 生成的可视化结果中安排线路门的放置？"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:224
msgid ""
"Try ``lcompress=True`` or ``rcompress=True`` option in "
":py:meth:`tensorcircuit.circuit.Circuit.tex` API to make the circuit "
"align from the left or from the right."
msgstr "在 :py:meth:`tensorcircuit.circuit.Circuit.tex` API 中尝试 ``lcompress=True`` 或 ``rcompress=True`` 选项，使线路向左或向右对齐。"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:226
msgid ""
"Or try ``c.unitary(0, unitary=tc.backend.eye(2), name=\"invisible\")`` to"
" add placeholder on the circuit which is invisible for circuit "
"visualization."
msgstr "或者尝试使用 ``c.unitary(0, unitary=tc.backend.eye(2), name=\"invisible\")`` 在线路上添加占位符，这在线路可视化中是不可见的。"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:230
msgid "How many different formats for the circuit sample results?"
msgstr "线路采样结果有多少种不同的格式？"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:232
msgid ""
"When performing measurements or sampling in TensorCircuit-NG, there are "
"six different formats available for the results:"
msgstr "在 TensorCircuit-NG 中进行测量或采样时，结果有六种不同的可用格式："

#: ../../source/faq.rst:234
