#: ../../source/faq.rst:314
msgid "What is the long-term support (LTS) commitment for TensorCircuit-NG?"
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 的长期支持（LTS）承诺是什么？"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:316
msgid ""
"TensorCircuit-NG is committed to long-term maintenance and stability. We "
"ensure compatibility with the latest versions of major ML frameworks "
"(Numpy, TensorFlow, JAX, PyTorch) and provide timely updates to stay "
"aligned with the evolving Python scientific computing ecosystem. Our "
"priority is to provide a reliable, performant, and future-proof platform "
"for both research and production-grade quantum simulation tasks."
msgstr "TensorCircuit-NG 致力于长期维护和稳定性。我们确保与主要机器学习框架（NumPy、TensorFlow、JAX、PyTorch）的最新版本兼容，并提供及时更新以保持与不断演进的 Python 科学计算生态系统一致。我们的首要任务是为科学研究和生产级量子模拟任务提供一个可靠、高性能且面向未来的平台。"
